{"tid":886260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV解密！「哪種職業女性最常上魔鏡號」　女護理師排第3","createTime":"2018-11-02T03:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T03:32:31.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4978ddf9872b3bd534a5de372349af9266c7d1cd","tid":886260,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:15:37.000Z","msg":"日本AV產業發展蓬勃，其中片商「SOD」（Soft On Demand）旗下的魔鏡號廣受男性們熟知，魔鏡號以上街隨機尋找素人到車上「啪啪啪」的拍攝手法爆紅，而日前就有節目公布魔鏡號「上車職業最多的女性」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvJ9Nt8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvJ9Nt8.png&h=ae9905bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bYD9Nt9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbYD9Nt9.png&h=1c73de51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據了解魔鏡號其實是三菱Canter貨車改裝而成，變成SOD的移動式攝影棚，而車廂的一個面是單向玻璃，即從外部觀看時，車廂部份有其中一個面是鏡子，但該面在車廂內的如同玻璃，可以從內看見外面。而日本MBS電視台30日播出的《Gobu gobu》(ごぶごぶ)節目中，主持人濱田雅功跟知名女藝人YOU，一起窺探魔鏡號的秘密。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K013RV2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK013RV2.png&h=649ef00a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRH6PHJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRH6PHJ.png&h=40c8aab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n節目中也介紹了魔鏡號的內裝，不僅舖有地毯備有沙發，冷氣、浴室、淋浴設備，完全符合拍片需求，而根據統計「哪個地區的女性最常上魔鏡號」第一名是東京、其次是神奈川、第三是宮城；此外，「上車女性職業的TOP3」分別為女大生、保母、女護理師。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yyVcLgm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyyVcLgm.png&h=bc613753&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9aj9H2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9aj9H2.png&h=ddc1886a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GRZtiBo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGRZtiBo.png&h=296b46fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oMthWn4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoMthWn4.png&h=0b7e21ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjaXbWq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjaXbWq.png&h=5d50582e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f582b4bcc3c030107d6046d545768b6ab1a0acc","tid":886260,"uid":133529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:26:43.000Z","msg":"呢個系列最假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6da6a186c9bb022bf268adb2981cc437a16e3daf","tid":886260,"uid":107950,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:30:55.000Z","msg":"成日都見到d AV女優扮素人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6c97b815a144127011b019e62fd8ed1046b93d","tid":886260,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T03:32:31.000Z","msg":"有幾多係真素人丫，真正中出系列 (半中出嗰啲)<br />\n<br />\n個個女仔都有名有姓。"}]}